---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<section id="clients" class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container-content">
    <SectionHeading
      eyebrow="Clients"
      title="合作夥伴"
      description="從政府單位、金融機構、跨國品牌到教育機構，我們很榮幸曾與這些夥伴共同完成專案。"
    />

    <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 md:gap-3 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      {site.clients.map((c) => (
        <li class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-ink-700 bg-ink-50 border border-ink-100 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-50 hover:text-primary-700 hover:border-primary-200 transition-colors">
          {c}
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-8 text-center text-xs text-ink-400">以上為部分合作夥伴名單，未依合作時序或規模排列。</p>
  </div>
</section>
